            <title>[LU-9024] conf-sanity test_63: FAIL: ldisk inode size is too big, 3 objs per page</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9024</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;conf-sanity test 63 failed as follows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== conf-sanity test 63: Verify each page can at least hold 3 ldisk inodes == 07:38:31 (1482565111)
CMD: trevis-46vm7 awk &apos;/ldiskfs_inode_cache/ { print \$5 }&apos; /proc/slabinfo
3 ldisk inodes per page
CMD: trevis-46vm7 awk &apos;/^(kmalloc|size)-128 / { print \$5 }&apos; /proc/slabinfo
 conf-sanity test_63: @@@@@@ FAIL: ldisk inode size is too big, 3 objs per page 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

